      ENZBDNZAOPQUGBDNZAOPUKAORSUHDMUIULAOUGBUHDTUAUFEMZULUKAOUMUGUJBDUECUFETUB
      UAFGHABCUCUD $.
      $( [16-Oct-1999] $)

